    "The corresponding hyperparameters are provided in table 9.",
    "Zebra Zebra is a token-based autoregressive model that combines a VQ-VAE for discretizing spatial fields with a causal transformer for modeling temporal dynamics.",
    "At each time step, it autoregressively predicts discrete latent tokens corresponding to the next frame, allowing for uncertainty quantification through stochastic sampling in latent space.",
